Gécamines and ENRC Africa Holdings have completed a transaction that sets the foundations for a redefined collaboration within their JV Boss Mining. The transaction in particular comprises: Gécamines welcomes this new achievement, as part of its strategy of consensual
redefinition of its partnerships, aiming at reaching a better sharing of the revenues and returns for Gécamines, as well as for the Democratic Republic of the Congo and the impacted communities.